#### NEW PAGE ####

<a id="C2"></a>
This cl<span class="title">a</span>ssification includes material related
~~to the recording of Hadith and <span class="title">b</span>iographies of reporters.
- TXT: Text
The original texts of all Hadith books are in Arabic, but this
~~classification is for translated works.
- USU: Usul
The terminology and explanation of Mustalah writings (Science of Hadith)
~~come into this category.
- WRI: Writings
All other general works on Islam that deal specifically with aspects of
~~the Hadith and Sunnah are classified in this category.
ملاحظة: - طبعت أسماء الكتب بالحرف الأسود، أما أسماء البحوث المنشورة في
~~المجلات فهي بالحروف المائلة.

